comments: Awesome teacher, definitely would recommend her to anyone.
TAKE HER!!! She makes learning so easy!
I was just awful at math before attending this class. She is super easy to understand, explains everything perfectly, and is willing to help everyone. Probably one of my favorite teachers so far.
Very slow and easy to keep up with
The best professor I have had at UMD. She is always willing to help and is actually good at explaining material during lectures and during office hours.

Very helpful instructor and personable- I\'m not much into math, but she made it seem easy to understand and do-able. She tries to make it minimumly boring. If you attend class and do the homework- you will be rewarded with a good grade. Highly recommended.

Randi is an AMAZING professor! She makes sure you understand the material and cares about your grade to help you pass. I got over 100% in her class, and I am usually one to fail math courses. Very approachable, and HIGHLY recommended. Very funny, too!
Its hard not to pass this class if you know the material and do your homework. Very willing to help and very approachable.
